## **Implementation Tips**
1. **Font Loading**: Use Google Fonts or similar services to load **Space Grotesk** efficiently. Include fallback fonts like Arial or Helvetica to ensure compatibility.
   ```html
   <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
   ```

2. **Responsive Design**: Adjust font sizes dynamically using CSS media queries to cater to different screen sizes.
   ```css
   @media (max-width: 768px) {
       h1 { font-size: 32px; }
       p { font-size: 14px; }
   }
   ```

3. **Accessibility**: Ensure sufficient contrast ratios between text and background colors to meet WCAG guidelines.
